==English==

===Noun===
'''[[solar]] [[wind]]'''

# The [[outflow]] of [[charge]]d [[particle]]s from the solar [[corona]] into [[space]]. Because of the high [[temperature]] of the particles of the corona, they are moving at speeds higher than the solar [[escape velocity]].

